Regal's The Fuel Eau de Toilette - 100 ml Price: Rs.649

Regal brings to you this perfume named 'The Fuel' which will ignite your senses keeping up with its name. This refreshing perfumed spray has an Eau de Toilette concentration which is a mixture of crisp fragrances like lemon tangerine and lavender as the top notes. The base notes of this perfumed spray are patchouli and oakmoss which would keep you energetic and refreshed for the whole day. Coriander and juniper serve as the heart notes of this perfume and bring it close enough to the nature. As this perfume has a light and enigmatic scent you would love to wear it around wherever you go. Add this balmy perfume from Regal to your collection of exclusive fragrances and smell great whenever you spray it. Regal The Fuel Perfume EDT Specifications.
